{"tid":2118864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［一週年 國際線］警員向外媒記者惡斥：Shut Up ！！","createTime":"2020-07-21T18:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T18:41:21.000Z","uid":219007,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b83c297d0b081bb985f1da2bf1eb7cc8cb7cea3e","tid":2118864,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/ZREGDGPD5A5Y4O5HXTXH57FV7M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FZREGDGPD5A5Y4O5HXTXH57FV7M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=1b5fb3a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FZREGDGPD5A5Y4O5HXTXH57FV7M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=85ca67b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/ZREGDGPD5A5Y4O5HXTXH57FV7M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n舊年元朗白衣人恐襲無辜市民，當日遲到39分鐘先現身嘅警員，唔止對手持木棍藤條嘅白衣暴徒視而不見，仲同佢哋搭晒膊頭。事至今日都仲未能夠釋疑，更已經喺市民心中留低深深烙印，繼日前有區議員就呢件事發起分組遊行，適逢7.21一周年，再有市民繼續企出嚟發聲。<br />\n<br />\n警方嘅截查行動一如既往，除咗多番查市民，記者都唔例外。雖然PPRB聲稱只係為咗搵出假記者，會尊重記者採訪工作，但唔知係咪深知已得到「港版國安法」護法，在場有位警員竟然聲大夾惡咁兇一位外媒記者叫佢「shut up！」<br />\n<br />\n睇返當時有位外國記者喺直播期間俾警員截停搜查，負責搜查嗰位警員可能知自己唔省鏡，係咁叫佢熄機（turn off your phone），又話而家警告緊佢，仲威嚇話「If you don't stop your video recording, I will arrest you！（如果你唔停止錄影，我就會拉你）」面對理據咁空泛嘅要求，嗰位外媒記者梗係想問多兩句，點知嗰位警員突然聲大大咁叫佢「shut up！」可能佢已經將識嘅句子用晒，驚再講落去R盡腦汁都應唔到機，有辱警隊形象，先至咁火爆。<br />\n<br />\n問返PPRB高振邦，先知原來佢哋係驚有「唔係記者嘅人混咗入去，可能違反599（G）限聚令」，所以先要截查記者。但現場所見，有逾30位「執法中」嘅警員都冇保持社交距離，而家疫情肆虐，八方只希望如燒生所言，唔好中招啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0HMOQo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0HMOQo.png&h=40fca5a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>Btw 蘋果記者做吓功課先唔該<br />\n個鬼仔係癲狗日報記者黎</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9268e5a5d8ff94c15f7c9c0e38ad6916bc5933","tid":2118864,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"識講英文, 叻叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b68545c7542aa9643a5659b6dcaafd8e4bcbf50","tid":2118864,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:27:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60310c04332cc0acd8be010ef6e922857fb1c378","tid":2118864,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係myradio果個julian黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb5f3301fd9ecedcd3613456a58a6338142d10b","tid":2118864,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:28:19.000Z","msg":"外媒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瘋狗日報黎架"},{"pid":"2f174c35db3edf6c73de81225d819db751372f60","tid":2118864,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b68545c7542aa9643a5659b6dcaafd8e4bcbf50","tid":2118864,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:27:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"得啦<br />\n睇同碌撚有關係既野=分化抹黑=五毛<br />\n明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501c4f64b3c7effa9377d4b301a12954617357d5","tid":2118864,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:30:42.000Z","msg":"南北朝終於識英文，唔使叫鬼佬講中文"},{"pid":"de5c26aca09fd3d27e196492bb1104